"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-05-20-chelsea-make-decision-enzo-fernandezs-olympics-participation-20876771\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Chelseahave reportedly grantedEnzo Fernandezpermission to join Argentina's squad for theOlympicsin what could be a very busy summer for the midfielder.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.413899788600009e-19, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old missed Chelsea's last sixPremier Leaguegames of the season afterundergoing surgery on a long-standing groin issuebut has been included in his nation's squad for the Copa America.\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5641434692543773e-24, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lionel Scaloni named his provisional 29-man squad on Monday and Fernandez made the cut, though he could be one of three players to drop out of the final squad if he does not prove his fitness over the coming weeks.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 349, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Scaloni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lionel Scaloni\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Scaloni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Scaloni\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world champions have two World Cup qualifiers early next month, against Ecuador and Guatemala, before kicking off their Copa America campaign against Canada on June 21.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4205135428954455e-23, \"text\": \"Ecuador\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.096474332493071e-14, \"text\": \"Guatemala\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998181997564, \"rank\": 1.8179990638271424e-07, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fernandez is also eligible to play at the Olympics, which follows straight after the Copa America, as he was under the age of 23 at the start of the season.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clubs are under no obligation to release players for the tournament, but, according towidespread reports in Argentina, Chelsea have given Fernandez permission to take part.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.413899788600009e-19, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5641434692543773e-24, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a somewhat surprising decision, with the Copa America final taking place on July 14 and Argentina's first group game at the Olympics kicking off just 10 days later against Morocco.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.413899788600009e-19, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.637410260793974e-23, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro's Head of Sport James Goldman delivers punchy analysis, transfer talk and his take on the week's biggest stories direct to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Goldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q28389\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up here, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, if Argentina, who are taking the tournament very seriously, make it to the final, that match will be played on August 11 - exactly one week before the new Premier League season kicks off.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.413899788600009e-19, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentina Under-23s boss Javier Mascherano is keen for as many of the nation's top talents to be involved as possible and that makes Fernandez - the only still U23-eligible player from the World Cup-winning squad - a particularly important selection.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.413899788600009e-19, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javier Mascherano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_under-23_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.681128385253869e-21, \"text\": \"U23\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_under-23_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_under-23_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about his possible involvement earlier this month, the Chelsea midfielder said: 'I have the possibility of going and I would love to go to the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1958, \"end\": 1965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5641434692543773e-24, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is Chelsea's decision, and I have not talked about it yet.'\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2067, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5641434692543773e-24, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other players who are believed to have been granted approval to take part are Brighton's Valentin Barco, Porto's Alan Varela and Fiorentina forward Lucas Beltran.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2203, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"score\": 0.9813093446022373, \"rank\": 0.019046649738908208, \"text\": \"Brighton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\"}, {\"begin\": 2223, \"end\": 2228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CD_Barco\", \"score\": 0.9999992516694036, \"rank\": 7.199873784913807e-07, \"text\": \"Barco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CD_Barco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CD_Barco\"}, {\"begin\": 2230, \"end\": 2235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Porto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.356552254393006e-27, \"text\": \"Porto\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Porto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Porto\"}, {\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Varela\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alan Varela\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Varela\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Varela\"}, {\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7983280557923077e-25, \"text\": \"Fiorentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\"}, {\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\", \"score\": 0.9936437405065649, \"rank\": 0.006222886296499078, \"text\": \"Lucas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teams are also allowed to bring three players over the age limit and,while Lionel Messi is believed to have turned down an invitein order to give younger players a chance to represent their nation, Mascherano still has some star players up his sleeve.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2371, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0341654438362918e-76, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aston Villa goalkeeper Emiliano Martinez is expected to be one of the three over-age players along with veteran defender Nicolas Otamendi, while the final spot is a toss-up between Manchester City's Julian Alvarez and Inter Milan striker Lautaro Martinez.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2542, \"end\": 2553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9858626012162747e-18, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Mart\\u00ednez\", \"score\": 0.9999999728756851, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emiliano Martinez\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Mart\\u00ednez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Mart\\u00ednez\"}, {\"begin\": 2723, \"end\": 2738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999600001684715, \"rank\": 4.000143156429477e-05, \"text\": \"Manchester City\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2760, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inter_Milan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.273402230160617e-28, \"text\": \"Inter Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inter_Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inter_Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 2780, \"end\": 2787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lautaro\", \"score\": 0.8321969971153188, \"rank\": 0.20163855849771792, \"text\": \"Lautaro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lautaro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lautaro\"}, {\"begin\": 2788, \"end\": 2796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\", \"score\": 0.9999857218977709, \"rank\": 1.4278269293468326e-05, \"text\": \"Martinez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking earlier this year, Martinez said of a possible Olympics call-up: 'If there is one thing I am missing with the national team, it is winning the Olympics.'\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\", \"score\": 0.9999857218977709, \"rank\": 1.4278269293468326e-05, \"text\": \"Martinez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tippy_Martinez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentina have a proud history at the Olympics and won the tournament in consecutive Games in 2004 and 2008.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.413899788600009e-19, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The likes of Roberto Ayala and Gabriel Heinze were the over-age players two decades ago, with Carlos Tevez, Javier Saviola and Mascherano himself also in the squad.\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3086, \"end\": 3099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roberto_Ayala\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roberto Ayala\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roberto_Ayala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roberto_Ayala\"}, {\"begin\": 3104, \"end\": 3118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Heinze\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Heinze\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Heinze\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Heinze\"}, {\"begin\": 3167, \"end\": 3179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Tevez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Tevez\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Tevez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Tevez\"}, {\"begin\": 3181, \"end\": 3195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Saviola\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javier Saviola\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Saviola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Saviola\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years later, the ex-Liverpool midfielder was one of the over-age players, along with Juan Roman Riquelme, while Pablo Zabaleta, Angel Di Maria, Sergio Aguero and Messi were all part of an astonishingly talented squad.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3329, \"end\": 3348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Rom\\u00e1n_Riquelme\", \"score\": 0.9999999998449312, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Juan R